[src:service-workers/api-clients] This feature is well established and works across many devices and browser versions.
[src:service-workers/api-clients] It’s been available across browsers since April 2018.
[src:service-workers/api-clients] The `Clients` interface provides access to `Client` objects.
[src:service-workers/api-clients] Access it via `self`.clients within a service worker.
